" map carriage return to create new todo entry
autocmd filetype taskpaper :nnoremap <buffer> <C-m> o- 
autocmd filetype taskpaper :inoremap <buffer> <C-m> <ESC>o- 
autocmd filetype taskpaper :nnoremap <buffer> o o- 
autocmd filetype taskpaper :nnoremap <buffer> O O- 

